{"tid":542843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過地產鋪聽到班大陸人評論香港樓價，香港樓真係好平..","createTime":"2018-01-28T01:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T01:44:20.000Z","uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a254932b81910687fd6bee1f20eb716f582e57ec","tid":542843,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T01:30:25.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n今日經過地產鋪,見到有班大陸人喺度討論香港樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">［他媽的香港房子才一萬多元，我老家現在也要兩萬多了。香港真是他媽的窮］<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n［深圳現在最貴的房子要10多萬元一平方了，香港最貴的房子連深圳邊皮也不是」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「我鄉下的老兄，在香港住公屋，但是他在老家擁有的房子呎價也要二萬元了。他跟我說，說香港人經常歧視他窮，那是天大的笑話。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「我們下次來香港，一齊來買香港的房子吧，一人一間，聽說香港人也窮得買不起房子，讓香港人羨慕一下。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n討論完樓市，班大陸人拖住幾箱黃道益雙飛人上返深圳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港樓市真靠大陸人頂住,先去到咁高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>90後情侶擬斥4球入市 女友笑認泊到好碼頭 </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180127/57761119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57761119&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9e0c50a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57761119&h=4318287d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180127/57761119</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static